nodes.text: A pilot from Pamarthe operated during the time of the New Republic. During her later life, she was present at a cantina on Pamarthe where Greer Sonnel, a native Pamarthen, drank Port in a Storm. Later, she was confronted by Sonnel and her friend, Joph Seastriker, when they asked about jobs that were available. The pilot informed them that were many runs to and from Daxam Four. Sonnel and Seastriker happily took the job, thanking her, but the pilot told them to thank her after dealing with the Amaxines.
